body.p:
The incidence of IIIC cases decreased 34.8% after 2012 and rebounded 82.6% after 2015, compared to 4.5% and 3.8% respectively for all comers excluding IIIC. For IIIC, 100 patients (25.4%) had a family history of prostate cancer, 191 (44.52%) had a pre-treatment prostate-specific antigen (PSA) level of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
